{"type":"message","id":"7a7a0d1d","parentId":"8e09d896","timestamp":"2026-04-26T04:55:23.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"RTX 2080 Ti 实际显存是 11GB（22528 MiB ≈ 11GB），但 MEMORY.md 里记录的是 4GB GDDR6，这个记录明显有误。当前已用了约 11GB（20146 MiB），只剩约 1.8GB。\n\nComfyUI 跑 Stable Diffusion 确实比较吃显存，特别是如果同时还有其他进程在占用显存的话。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n查了一下，你的 RTX 2080 Ti 实际有 **11GB 显存**（不是之前记错的 4GB），但当前已经用了约 **11GB**，只剩 **1.8GB** 空闲。\n\n所以昨天 ComfyUI 画不出来很可能是因为显存被占满了。ComfyUI 跑 Stable Diffusion 起步就要 4-6GB，高分辨率或大模型更吃。\n\n你现在显存基本满了，要不要看看是什么在占用？还是先清一下再试？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-27b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777179310793,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ozx1eslr2ha52j4ys3n90i"}}
