{"type":"message","id":"b9a240a5","parentId":"9125c65e","timestamp":"2026-04-26T06:48:06.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ollama 服务在运行（版本 0.21.2），模型列表中有 9 个 cloud 模型，配置中已经添加了 `gpt-oss:120b-cloud`。\n\n但用户说\"加不上\"、\"连不通\"、\"对话一直卡在那儿\"，可能有几个问题：\n\n1. Ollama 的 cloud 模型需要网络连接，如果网络有问题就会卡住\n2. 配置中的 apiKey 可能不对（Ollama 通常不需要 apiKey）\n3. 模型 ID 格式可能有问题（Ollama 的模型 ID 在 OpenAI 兼容接口中可能需要去掉 `:latest` 之类的后缀）\n\n让我先测试一下 Ollama 的 OpenAI 兼容接口是否正常工作：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOllama 服务在运行，模型也有 9 个。问题出在连接上。先测一下 Ollama 的 OpenAI 兼容接口能不能通：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"522972761","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1/models 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); [print(m['id']) for m in d.get('data',[])]\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"OpenAI API 接口不通\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777186063022,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cq2j9dk24a9rskazykaoc"}}
