{"type":"message","id":"8b88173f","parentId":"ad9c02f0","timestamp":"2026-04-26T06:48:30.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ollama 的 OpenAI 兼容接口是通的，模型列表也能获取到。那问题可能是：\n\n1. apiKey 配置不对 —— Ollama 不需要 apiKey，但 OpenClaw 配置中写了 `\"apiKey\": \"ollama\"`\n2. 模型 ID 格式问题 —— Ollama 的模型 ID 在 OpenAI 接口中可能需要调整\n3. 网络连接问题 —— cloud 模型需要访问外部 API\n\n让我试试用 curl 直接测试 Ollama 的 chat completions 接口：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n接口是通的。问题可能是 apiKey 配置不对（Ollama 不需要密钥），或者 cloud 模型访问外部 API 有网络问题。我试一下直接调用：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"684090505","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"gpt-oss:120b-cloud\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"hi\"}],\"max_tokens\":50}' 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('choices',[{}])[0].get('message',{}).get('content','no content'))\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"调用失败\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777186086609,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3ruz8056pe5n5rdaage05m"}}
