{"type":"message","id":"a81097df","parentId":"028a104d","timestamp":"2026-04-26T07:26:54.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The logs show that the config was successfully hot-reloaded with all Ollama models. The gateway restarted successfully. The direct API test to Ollama worked fine - it returned a proper response.\n\nThe issue the user experienced earlier was:\n1. The `apiKey: \"ollama\"` was causing auth issues - now removed\n2. Only 1 model was configured - now all 9 are added\n\nThe direct curl test shows Ollama is working. The `ollama ps` shows no running models because these are cloud models - they don't run locally, they proxy to external APIs.\n\nLet me explain this to the user and confirm everything is working now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n配置已经全部生效了。刚才卡着的原因找到了：\n\n1. **多余的 apiKey** —— Ollama 不需要认证，之前配了 `\"ollama\"` 导致每次请求都在等认证超时，现在去掉了\n2. **模型不全** —— 之前只加了 1 个，现在 9 个全在\n\nOllama 本身是通的（我刚直接测了能正常对话）。这些 `:cloud` 模型不走本地显存，走的是外部 API，所以 `ollama ps` 显示空是正常的。\n\n你现在可以试试用 `/model` 切到 Ollama 模型对话。如果还卡，告诉我切哪个模型卡的，我再查。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777188362911,"responseId":"chatcmpl-nzoualx7ba10v4sn0ku0de"}}
